', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/137138/', '', 'Acetaminophen, Ibuprofen, Celecoxib, Acetylsalicylic acid, Naloxone', 'Golimumab, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Tacrolimus, More', 1767369485);
